data.name: grdINV4001.QuerySQL
data.value: -- INV4001 SELECT A.PKINV4001 , A.CHURI_DATE , A.CHURI_BUSEO , A.IPGO_TYPE , A.CHURI_SEQ , A.JAERYO_GUBUN , A.REMARK FROM INV4001 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.CHURI_DATE BETWEEN :f_from_date AND :f_to_date ORDER BY A.CHURI_DATE DESC , A.CHURI_BUSEO , A.IPGO_TYPE , A.CHURI_SEQ

data.name: xEditGridCell21.UserSQL
data.value: SELECT B.CODE , B.CODE_NAME FROM INV0102 B , INV0101 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.CODE_TYPE = 'IPGO_TYPE' -- AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.CODE_TYPE = A.CODE_TYPE ORDER BY B.SORT_KEY

data.name: grdINV4002.QuerySQL
data.value: -- INV4002 SELECT A.PKINV4002 AS PKINV4002 , A.FKINV4001 AS FKINV4001 , A.JAERYO_CODE AS JAERYO_CODE , B.JAERYO_NAME AS JAERYO_NAME , A.IPGO_QTY AS IPGO_QTY --, B.SUBUL_DANUI AS IPGO_DANUI , FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME ( 'ORD_DANUI', B.SUBUL_DANUI) IPGO_DANUI_NAME , A.IPGO_DANGA AS IPGO_DANGA , A.REMARK AS REMARK , A.IPGO_QTY * A.IPGO_DANGA AS SUM_DANGA FROM INV0110 B , INV4002 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.FKINV4001 = :f_fkinv4001 -- AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.JAERYO_CODE = A.JAERYO_CODE ORDER BY B.JAERYO_NAME

data.name: cbxActor.UserSQL
data.value: -- DRG USER LIST SELECT '' USER_ID , '' USER_NM FROM SYS.DUAL UNION SELECT A.USER_ID , A.USER_NM FROM ADM3200 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.USER_GROUP = 'DRG' AND NVL(A.USER_END_YMD, '9998/12/31') >= SYSDATE ORDER BY USER_ID NULLS FIRST
